<div id="review_3487065975" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3487065975" />
    <a title="Elham" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/45758171-elham"><img alt="Elham" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1579428166p2/45758171.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3487065975?book_show_action=true">Aug 24, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Elham" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Elham" href="/user/show/45758171-elham">Elham</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/43327402">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3487065975" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7104268453778699053">It is more like a book to reflect on nature and art and beauty.. some images and descriptions are absolutely beautiful.. but I am not sure I got any of the characters, they are all flat... the narrator and main character is a painter who embarks on a journey in the rural Japan, but who never draws one paiting, except maybe at the last page where he gets an idea for his next painting..</span>

          </span>
